{"tid":2119422,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"JUPAS 科大商科 揀之前你問我答","createTime":"2020-07-22T05:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T06:04:56.000Z","uid":190741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e022580dd72ade507845becf57dbedf9f6e5b66e","tid":2119422,"uid":190741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:51:04.000Z","msg":"有咩關於科大商科可以放低問下<br />\n<br />\n利申：小弟JUPAS直接入科大商科<br />\n中學冇讀bafs 大學跟得有少少辛苦<br />\n預咗呢度workload好大 讀書氛圍都幾大壓力<br />\n但你話揾工個名係有睇少少嘅 不過就自己諗清楚係唔係要揀科大。"},{"pid":"d19cef0065f8c6e2c5ce6b67153602b3d57b9549","tid":2119422,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:52:21.000Z","msg":"俾你揀多次會唔會入科大，定會揀中大或港大？"},{"pid":"65f7028622f10fafdfcbc944eca4968daf5241cb","tid":2119422,"uid":235801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"讀phy chem入BBA, 會唔會handle唔到"},{"pid":"8525e6e780665ef00693e646ccfba91359cc9efb","tid":2119422,"uid":190741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d19cef0065f8c6e2c5ce6b67153602b3d57b9549","tid":2119422,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:52:21.000Z","msg":"俾你揀多次會唔會入科大，定會揀中大或港大？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:18:01.000Z","msg":"有得再揀 我會揀中大或者港大<br />\n見朋友仔佢哋啲course都幾好grade同唔太大workload<br />\n讀書氛圍起碼冇咁緊張 可以過返多少少所謂u life"},{"pid":"a781b3853d4e065373c5b65899906c9085c8c3b1","tid":2119422,"uid":77916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:20:09.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\nJS4240 中大會計 CUHK PACC 放榜問答區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2118518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2118518</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"19baa0bda7773aa35e8126ff02cd7e040246b814","tid":2119422,"uid":190741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65f7028622f10fafdfcbc944eca4968daf5241cb","tid":2119422,"uid":235801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"讀phy chem入BBA, 會唔會handle唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:21:25.000Z","msg":"我當年Phy Chem Econ入BBA <br />\n頭兩年會要求你讀所有唔同major既course(e.g Econ, Acct, Finance...)<br />\n除咗acct我個人覺得跟得比較辛苦 佢教嘅嘢係好似expect你中學一定讀過bafs咁 所以要啲時間自己學返<br />\n其他major既course都還可以"},{"pid":"416994f2e608652a040dc0f10b4d92e4b6e860b0","tid":2119422,"uid":235801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19baa0bda7773aa35e8126ff02cd7e040246b814","tid":2119422,"uid":190741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65f7028622f10fafdfcbc944eca4968daf5241cb","tid":2119422,"uid":235801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"讀phy chem入BBA, 會唔會handle唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:21:25.000Z","msg":"我當年Phy Chem Econ入BBA <br />\n頭兩年會要求你讀所有唔同major既course(e.g Econ, Acct, Finance...)<br />\n除咗acct我個人覺得跟得比較辛苦 佢教嘅嘢係好似expect你中學一定讀過bafs咁 所以要啲時間自己學返<br />\n其他major既course都還可以"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:39:26.000Z","msg":"咁bba嘅出路如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3743cea0af72f01b47487b100c60a254ba6c2b","tid":2119422,"uid":93633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:08:13.000Z","msg":"想問問如果報咗JS5300工商管理，要幾多GPA先可以year2轉去讀econ(JS5311)?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5442e134867ea83df8bb304dafc78996418991e","tid":2119422,"uid":205244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd3743cea0af72f01b47487b100c60a254ba6c2b","tid":2119422,"uid":93633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:08:13.000Z","msg":"想問問如果報咗JS5300工商管理，要幾多GPA先可以year2轉去讀econ(JS5311)?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:13:27.000Z","msg":"econ course 個grade 靚就得"},{"pid":"2b30eb423c219