:2119422,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9512a861c4fec540cf622d88cb93b685580ee50","tid":2119422,"uid":7095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"Econ 好易入 唔算熱門科"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"利申：Econ Major"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:52:07.000Z","msg":"Ching 有冇double maj"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"Acct"},{"pid":"cfecdd0840969463168778cc7fefd6f206988761","tid":2119422,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T06:04:56.000Z","msg":"借舊文一貼<br />\n<br />\n各位DSE既同學仔大家好, 唔知你地諗好入咩大學同讀咩科未呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日小妹我開呢個post就係為大家打打氣, 順便同大家介紹下科大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 科大名聲好, 排名高<br />\n科大, 別名Asia MIT, 香港第0<br />\n根據QS排名, 科大曾經超越港大成為左香港第0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n科大既engine同business係17年既排名更加比港大個排名高唔少<br />\n第時入到科大比d豬朋狗友問你出路, 你都絕對可以好驕傲咁講我讀科大啊, 相信唔少人都會讀你叻仔叻女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 科大學術氣氛好<br />\n大家咁辛苦入到大學梗係想追求更多既知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n科大係呢方面就訓練到學生十分著重讀書, 每星期都安排唔同既功課同測驗比學生溫故而知新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你可以見到既就係同學落堂去就擁埋去教授到問書, 問完就會去拉把溫習, 同學之間都會有各種既學術討論, 係咁既氛圍底下, 你GPA都自然會高啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 科大男女比例均衡<br />\n街外人經常流傳科大係咩少林寺啊, 格劍聖地等<br />\n呢d其實都係唔太正確既講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以business school為例, 16intake男女比例為47:53, 53既仲要係女黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試想像下上堂acct堂, 前後左右都係女既話, 你每堂都有動力去上啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://undergrad.bm.ust.hk/eng/why/students/our_students/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fundergrad.bm.ust.hk%2Feng%2Fwhy%2Fstudents%2Four_students%2Findex.jsp&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=cab45a07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://undergrad.bm.ust.hk/eng/why/students/our_students/index.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n再聽下幾個名人分享科大:<br />\n1. 嶺大分數, 三大名氣/engine就是ust(鍵盤騎士, 2015) <br />\n相信大家都聽過呢類型既說話, 想用大學黎證明自己能力, 科大絕對係你既首選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 港大張xx/鏗x都同鍵騎有唔少交情, 佢地都好支持鍵騎入讀科大civil, 認為係明智之選<br />\n<br />\n各位DSE同學仔聽完係咪心動呢, 如果係就請立即登入JUPAS Account, 更改你既選擇至JS5xxxx (任何你心儀既科大科目)<br />\n祝福你地DSE都能順利渡過, 9月係科大呢個大家庭見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}